The most effective way to train melee skills in [[free-to-play]] worlds is to use [[Alt|alternative character]]s. Killing unarmoured 1 [[defence]] level players in [[Clan Wars]] free-for-all area or [[Castle Wars]] is among the fastest ways to gain combat experience, although these training methods usually come with a cost, and are free of any loot. Since experience in [[PvP]] combat [[Combat#PvP bonus experience|scales with opponent's combat level]], training on high level combat pures is the most effective.

